{"tid":1801850,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"任何可以宣傳既微細既地方都唔可以放過！","createTime":"2019-12-29T03:43:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T03:53:59.000Z","uid":202994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"00344bced356e0a7699ac50285313d79b6a8ecf3","tid":1801850,"uid":202994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:43:29.000Z","msg":"1月1元旦遊行啊 個風吹得仲細過1208個次 <br />\n聖誕係咪玩得好開心 唔洗抗爭啦 <br />\n仲有成班手足係海外係荔枝角係被預約拘捕架<br />\n所有地方所有social media可以做文宣既地方都要做<br />\n你見到隻老鼠曱甴係地下爬 見到烏蠅昆蟲飛都唔該幫我貼張文宣落去<br />\n去廁格抆紙巾唔該攝兩張文宣落去<br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地啲ig icon都換埋文宣</span></div></span></strong></strong> <span style=\"color: red;\">務求令你啲朋友唔洗撳入story都見到1月1元旦遊行</span><br />\n集思廣益下 連儂場個啲當然要做 希望大家可以有更多唔同既idea 任何地方都唔好睇少 多一個人見到就多一修力量<br />\n下面呢張圖真係啱晒做icon<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ph7n6aF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fph7n6aF.jpg&h=4835c0e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HevH6aH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHevH6aH.jpg&h=47f3562c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"167a3a1037d8fd3b18d4d4c30e699518587e0cb4","tid":1801850,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:46:55.000Z","msg":"仲有記住airdrop<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈的障礙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801188</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a6f84d56ecf7ef1f7a7f924093e323a0c078e133","tid":1801850,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:53:59.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n推薦個App 俾大家<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.votes.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.votes.hk&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNWWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=6e10a30f\" data-auto-link target=\"_bla